  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">In a scale model of an office building, a length of <math alttext=\"1\"><mn>1</mn>\n</math> inch is equivalent to a length of <math alttext=\"StartFraction 17 Over 3 EndFraction\"><mfrac><mn>17</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac></math> feet in the actual office building. If a length in the actual office building measures <math alttext=\"x\"><mi>x</mi>\n</math> feet, which expression represents the corresponding length, in inches, in the model in terms of <math alttext=\"x\"><mi>x</mi>\n</math>?</p>",
  "answerOptions": [
